{{doc/start}}
Renders a single version history entry, showing a bold version label followed by a bullet list of changes. Stack multiple instances in the <code>== History ==</code> section of a page, one per version, in reverse chronological order (newest first).

== Usage ==
<pre>
{{History|VERSION|
* Change description.
* Another change.
}}
</pre>

== Parameters ==
{| class="wikitable"
! Parameter !! Description !! Type !! Status
|-
| <code>1</code> || Version identifier, e.g. <code>Update 2 (Early Access)</code> or <code>0.4.3</code>. Displayed in bold followed by a colon. Can be a plain string or a wikilink. || String || Required
|-
| <code>2</code> || Wikitext bullet list of changes introduced in this version. Each item should start with <code>*</code> on its own line. || Wikitext || Required
|}

== Examples ==
<pre>
{{History|Update 2: Galactic Commerce (Early Access)|
* Added Galactic Market.
* Reworked shipping pad throughput.
}}

{{History|Update 1 (Early Access)|
* Initial Early Access release.
}}
</pre>

== Notes ==
* Place entries in reverse chronological order — newest version at the top of the History section.
* The version label can be a wikilink to the relevant patch note page: <code><nowiki>[[Update 2 (Early Access)|Update 2: Galactic Commerce]]</nowiki></code>.
* Styles are loaded from <code>[[Template:History/styles.css]]</code>.
* This template replaces the older <code><nowiki>{{History table}}</nowiki></code> placeholder.
{{doc/end}}
